category: THE MANGER ZONE
category comment: 

clue: "Now when Jesus was born in" this town, "there came wise men from the east to Jerusalem"

response: Bethlehem

clue: "She brought forth her firstborn son... and laid him in a manger; because there was no room for them" at this place

response: the inn

clue: "When they had opened their treasures, they presented unto him gifts": these 3 items

response: gold, frankincense & myrrh

clue: "And when they were departed... the angel of the Lord" said take the child & his mom & "flee into" this present-day nation

response: Egypt

clue: This king "gathered all the chief priests and scribes of the people" & "demanded of them where Christ should be born"

response: King Herod

